"{\"correct\": \"no\", \"explanation\": \"The x parameter for the plt.text function is set to a datetime object, which is not in data coordinates as expected by the text API. The x parameter should correspond to a value from the data being plotted, which in this case is from df['C']. The datetime value should be converted to a numerical format that corresponds to the x-axis of the plot.\", \"patch\": \"17c17\\n< plt.text(datetime.datetime.strptime(\\\"2013-01-05\\\"), 0.5, \\\"SAMPLE\\\")\\n---\\n> plt.text(df['C'].iloc[4], 0.5, \\\"SAMPLE\\\")\\n\"}"